                  Beng Chin Ooi and
                  Chunyan Miao},
	title = {Knowledge is Power: Hierarchical-Knowledge Embedded Meta-Learning
                  for Visual Reasoning in Artistic Domains},
	booktitle = {{KDD} '21: The 27th {ACM} {SIGKDD} Conference on Knowledge Discovery
                  and Data Mining, Virtual Event, Singapore, August 14-18, 2021},
